    'Monday'    => 'Work',          'Monday' => 'Work',
    'Tuesday'   => 'Tacos',         'Tuesday' => 'Tacos',
    'Wednesday' => 'Waffles'        'Wednesday' => 'Waffles'
};                              };
```

[`PREMIUM`](command:phptools.activatewindow) が必要です

